argest and most far reaching events in history and not a word is said about it anymore. It was only 5 years ago.\n- Vaccines for Covid. Oops more proof every day they weren't ready.\n- Kyle Rittenhouse\n- George Floyd\n- Hunter's laptop\n- Biden's health\n- The current President was almost assassinated a handful of times and it was treated like someone snatching a purse.\n\nBut they are always sure they are right THIS time.", "author": "Relictus_Patriae", "created": 1771415037812, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "penguinjay1212", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Just a reminder that the side of \"intellectuals\" has been wrong about every major event in recent history. They dont talk about them, ever.", "last_comment_created": 1771432790418, "content": "<p>Here is a short list. Every time they say we are wrong or on the wrong side of history, remind them. Some of these I had to remind myself weren't fever dreams because they have memory holed them. Please, add your own.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Russia Collusion. Hillary bought fake info from a foreign spy.</li>\n<li>Ukraine impeachment. Better hide that money laundering, Democrats, and fast!</li>\n<li>COVID. One of the largest and most far reaching events in history and not a word is said about it anymore. It was only 5 years ago.</li>\n<li>Vaccines for Covid. Oops more proof every day they weren't ready.</li>\n<li>Kyle Rittenhouse</li>\n<li>George Floyd</li>\n<li>Hunter's laptop</li>\n<li>Biden's health</li>\n<li>The current President was almost assassinated a handful of times and it was treated like someone snatching a purse.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>But they are always sure they are right THIS time.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair